<L><PB N="69" REF="70">
But baffled thus! confe&s;s'd &s;o far below</L>
<L><HI>Uly&s;&s;es</HI>' &s;trength, as not to bend his bow!</L>
<L>How &s;hall all ages our attempt deride?<MILESTONE N="270"></L>
<L>Our weakne&s;s &s;corn? <HI>Antinous</HI> thus reply'd.</L>
