<L>The wa&s;te of years refunded in a day.<MILESTONE N="70"></L>
<L>'Till then thy wrath is ju&s;t&mdash;<HI>Uly&s;&s;es</HI> burn'd</L>
<L>With high di&s;dain, and &s;ternly thus return'd.</L>
