<L>And &s;econd all <HI>Eupithes</HI>' rage in&s;pir'd.</L>
<L><MILESTONE N="535">They ca&s;e their limbs in bra&s;s; to arms they run;</L>
<L>The broad effulgence blazes in the &s;un.</L>
<L>Before the city, in an ample plain,</L>
<L>They meet: <HI>Eupithes</HI> heads the frantic train.</L>
