<L><MILESTONE N="615">&startq;Forbear ye natives! your mad hands forbear</L>
<L>From mutual &s;laughter: <HI>Peace</HI> de&s;cends to &s;pare.&endq;</L>
<L>Fear &s;hook the nations. At the voice divine</L>
<L>They drop their jav'lins, and their rage re&s;ign,</L>
<L>All &s;catter'd round their glitt'ring weapons lie;</L>
<L><MILESTONE N="620">Some fall to earth, and &s;ome confus'dly fly.</L>
