<L>Swift as an eagle, as an eagle &s;trong.</L>
<L>But <HI>Jove</HI>'s red arm the burning thunder aims;</L>
<L>Before <HI>Minerva</HI> &s;hot the livid flames;</L>
<L><MILESTONE N="625">Blazing they fell, and at her feet expir'd:</L>
<L>Then &s;topt the Godde&s;s, trembled, and retir'd.</L>
<L><PB N="255" REF="252">
De&s;cended from the Gods! <HI>Uly&s;&s;es,</HI> cea&s;e;</L>
<L>Offend not <HI>Jove:</HI> Obey, and give the peace.</L>
